®In Loving Memory of Barbara Alice Harper
1934 2015
She was passionate about her gardening and enjoyed sharing
her love of nature and wildlife with family and friends"æ
ªFor Mary Lou Lancaster of Falmouth, Maine,
who loves London's gardens
almost as much as her husband loves her - 
on the occasion of their fortieth wedding anniversary
August 21st 1994"ø
